	<description>
		<p>With botfather you can create and run automation bots with ease.
		Automate your favorite Android, Browser and Desktop applications using bot scripts.
		Find scripts online or create your own using Botfathers convenient APIs.
		Botfather has image recognition, custom types and many more already built in.</p>
	</description>

